00:48:05.679 --> 00:48:10.479
I guess the kind of the way I look at it is I think the field of software engineering

00:48:10.479 --> 00:48:18.479
is, you know, essentially, maybe go like the difference between, you know, before the

00:48:18.479 --> 00:48:21.840
printing press or like before books, I'm trying to come with the right analogy, right?

00:48:21.840 --> 00:48:28.000
So like plenty of people, they read books, they read literature, they go to school to

00:48:28.000 --> 00:48:33.439
