00:48:46.239 --> 00:48:52.159
And so I think the field of software engineering is going to go from, you know, essentially,

00:48:52.159 --> 00:49:00.080
like the agent is doing all of the typing, but you're still doing most of the critical

00:49:00.159 --> 00:49:04.800
thinking about like, what is the proper shape and structure of the system essentially creating

00:49:04.800 --> 00:49:10.000
like the algebraic structure of like the layers that you're building.

