about Arrow and maybe since you're a mathematician, maybe something that appealed to you is that

00:50:07.360 --> 00:50:11.919
that notion of composability and like the interoperability and like the layering of

00:50:11.919 --> 00:50:14.879
software almost as a mathematical concept in a way.

